## Daily Development Workflow

### Backend only

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
docker-compose up -d postgres
alembic upgrade head
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000
# Optional: python -m app.worker
```

### Frontend only (backend already running)

```bash
cd frontend
nvm use 22
npm run dev
```

### Full stack

Open 3 terminals:

```bash
# Terminal 1: Postgres
docker-compose up -d postgres

# Terminal 2: Backend
source .venv/bin/activate
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000

# Terminal 3: Frontend
cd frontend && nvm use 22 && npm run dev
```

### Before pushing

```bash
# Backend tests
source .venv/bin/activate
pytest

# Frontend build check
cd frontend
npm run build
npm run lint
```

